2020年6月29日，[[巴基斯坦證券交易所|巴基斯坦證券交易所]]（{{lang|en|PSX}}）發生了'''襲擊事件'''。{{le|武裝分子|Militant}}投放手榴彈及無差別開火，造成至少三名守衛與一名{{le|副督察|Sub-inspector}}死亡及七人受傷。警方稱四名施襲者皆被擊斃。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pakistan stock exchange in Karachi under attack, say police|url=https://www.thenational.ae/world/asia/pakistan-stock-exchange-in-karachi-under-attack-say-police-1.1040934|access-date=2020-06-29|website=The National|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629061920/https://www.thenational.ae/world/asia/pakistan-stock-exchange-in-karachi-under-attack-say-police-1.1040934|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Gunmen attack Karachi stock exchange building in Pakistan |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/06/gunmen-attack-pakistan-stock-exchange-building-karachi-200629060634288.html |accessdate=2020-06-29 |work=www.aljazeera.com |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918133315/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/06/gunmen-attack-pakistan-stock-exchange-building-karachi-200629060634288.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=GEO>{{cite news |title='All terrorists killed,' police say after Pakistan Stock Exchange comes under gun and grenade attack |url=https://www.geo.tv/latest/295362-karachi-police-officers-injured-in-grenade-attack-outside-pakistan-stock-exchange-office |accessdate=2020-06-29 |work=www.geo.tv |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308055828/https://www.geo.tv/latest/295362-karachi-police-officers-injured-in-grenade-attack-outside-pakistan-stock-exchange-office |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=CNN |first1=Sophia Saifi |title=Multiple people dead after attack on Pakistan Stock Exchange |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/06/29/asia/karachi-pakistan-stock-exchange-attack-intl-hnk/index.html |accessdate=2020-06-29 |work=CNN |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308114510/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/06/29/asia/karachi-pakistan-stock-exchange-attack-intl-hnk/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==事發過程==
2020年6月29日早上10時02分，施襲者乘坐轎車抵達位於{{le|I·I·琼德里加路|I. I. Chundrigar Road}}的[[巴基斯坦證券交易所|巴基斯坦證券交易所]]。{{le|巴基斯坦民兵團|Pakistan Rangers}}總監稱10時10分時，四名施襲者已經全數被安全部隊擊斃<ref name=Dawn/>。他亦稱武裝分子“不僅打算殺戮，也計劃挾持人質”<ref>{{cite news |title=Gunmen Wage Deadly Battle at Pakistan Stock Exchange |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/29/world/asia/pakistan-stock-exchange-shooting.html |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308195259/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/29/world/asia/pakistan-stock-exchange-shooting.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。襲擊事件遭挫敗後，安全部隊隨即清場，現場在約30至35分鐘後恢復平靜<ref name=Dawn/>。

[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]警長告訴[[路透社|路透社]]指武裝分子乘坐一輛[[豐田卡羅拉|豐田卡羅拉]]抵達現場。他們攜自動步槍，並在施放一枚手榴彈後開始往證券交易所外的守衛亭開槍<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-06-29|title=Gunmen attack Pakistani stock exchange, six killed: police|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-attacks-idUSKBN2400IS|access-date=2020-06-29|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019225500/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-attacks-idUSKBN2400IS|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

官方消息稱守衛隨即反擊，並將四名施襲者擊斃，過程中有警員及安全部隊成員受傷。目擊者稱施襲者從停車場走來並向“每一個人開槍”。報導也稱大多數人逃過射殺，其中有人在鎖上的房間裡避難。《{{le|地理新聞|Geo News}}》稱交易所內的群眾從建築後門撤出現場<ref name=GEO/>。

事件共造成一名警員與三名守衛死亡<ref name="Dawn"/>，另有三名警員、兩名守衛及一名交易所僱員受傷<ref name=Samaa>{{cite news |title=Karachi stock exchange attack: Sindh Rangers say four terrorists killed |url=https://www.samaa.tv/news/pakistan/2020/06/pakistan-stock-exchange-karachi-attack/ |work=Samaa TV |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225102547/https://www.samaa.tv/news/pakistan/2020/06/pakistan-stock-exchange-karachi-attack/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。傷者被送入{{le|卡拉奇民事醫院|Dr. Ruth K. M. Pfau Civil Hospital Karachi}}治療<ref name=GEO/>。案發現場尋獲四個包裹，裡頭裝有四桿[[衝鋒槍|衝鋒槍]]、手榴彈、武器、水壺與[[椰棗|蜜棗]]<ref name=Samaa/>。

==反應==
證交所並無因襲擊事件而停止交易<ref name="Dawn">{{cite news |title=All 4 terrorists killed in attempt to storm Pakistan Stock Exchange compound in Karachi: Rangers |url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1565922/all-4-terrorists-killed-in-attempt-to-storm-pakistan-stock-exchange-compound-in-karachi-rangers |work=Dawn |date=2020-06-29 |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307233724/https://www.dawn.com/news/1565922/all-4-terrorists-killed-in-attempt-to-storm-pakistan-stock-exchange-compound-in-karachi-rangers |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ET">{{cite news |title=Seven killed in gun attack on Pakistan Stock Exchange |url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/2252502/seven-killed-in-gun-attack-on-pakistan-stock-exchange |work=The Express Tribune |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308214928/https://tribune.com.pk/story/2252502/seven-killed-in-gun-attack-on-pakistan-stock-exchange |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦如往常般準時閉市。{{le|KSE 100指數|KSE 100 Index}}閉市時走高242點（0.72%），收在34,181.80點。無論如何，事發後股市一度出現拋售潮，導致指數大跌220點至全日最低點，但隨後收復失地，大升267點至全日最高<ref>{{cite news |title=Stocks rally despite terror attack on PSX building |url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1566052 |work=Dawn |accessdate=2020-06-30 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019225521/https://www.dawn.com/news/1566052 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==作案動機==
2016年，中國牽頭的財團收購了巴基斯坦證券交易所40%的股份。襲擊發生後，[[俾路支解放軍|俾路支解放軍]]對此事件負責，該組織聲稱之所以襲擊就是因為該交易所是由一個中資財團部分持有。該組織同時警告中國，如果中國繼續剝削[[俾路支人|俾路支人民]]，該組織將發起針對中國的更多襲擊。中方對此次襲擊案表示譴責<ref>{{cite news|title=巴基斯坦證券交易所恐怖襲擊案　發動組織：因為由中資財團部分持有|url=https://inews.hket.com/article/2683352/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E8%B2%A1%E5%9C%98%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89|publisher=香港經濟日報|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019225527/https://inews.hket.com/article/2683352/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E8%B2%A1%E5%9C%98%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

